criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Patients with de novel AML in favorable and intermediate-risk group younger than 60 years old;
2. Peripheral blood stem cell harvesting was started if patients reached CR1 and MRD level was less than 0.1% without LAIPs after 1 to 2 courses of induction therapy and at least 2-3 courses of consolidation therapy including high-doses Ara-C;
3. ECOG=0,1.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1.Secondary AML, >60 years old;
2.AML in high-risk cytogenetic group;
3. to reach CR1 with more than 2 courses of induction;
4. >CR1 or MRD level >0.1% (including RQ-PCR test )and with FCM-LAIPs;
5.ECOG >=2.
